SkillSync Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 21/2/2025
Last Updated: 21/2/2025

1. Introduction

SkillSync ("we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you use our platform.

2. Data We Collect

We collect the following types of data:

Personal Information: Name, email, Pi username.

Transaction Data: Pi payments made through our platform.

Usage Data: Interactions with the platform, job postings, and messages.


3. How We Use Your Data

We use your data to:

Provide and improve the SkillSync platform.

Facilitate payments and transactions securely.

Communicate updates, support, and service-related notifications.


4. Third-Party Services

We integrate Pi Network's authentication and payment system.

We do not store Pi wallet credentials or private keys.


5. Data Security

We use security measures to protect your data, but users are responsible for securing their own accounts.

6. User Rights

You may request data deletion by contacting our support.

You can manage account information within the app.


7. Contact Us

For any privacy concerns, email: [viralethereum@gmail.com]

